OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUganda's tough anti-gay law
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchallenged in court        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, One of the world's harshest            
OL,6, anti-homosexuality laws is being       
OL,7, challenged in the Ugandan courts by    
OL,8, rights groups.                         
OL,10,FThe law has caused global outrage, with
OL,11,Fthe World Bank halting new loans to    
OL,12,FUganda and the US imposing visa        
OL,13,Frestrictions on key officials.         
OL,15,FAnyone convicted of being involved in  
OL,16,Fhomosexual acts face life imprisonment 
OL,17,Funder the law which was enacted in May.
OL,19,FRights groups have asked judges to     
OL,20,Fannul the law, arguing that it violated
OL,21,Fthe right to equality and dignity.     
